    "These instruments can try to measure, for example, satisfaction, ease of use perceived value, and emotions evoked by the system.",
    "An example of a questionnaire used to evaluate UX is AttrakDiff [69].",
    "For HCAI systems, questionnaires can help to understand how the users perceive AI behavior, the system's general utility, and vice versa.",
